profile: For over 40 years,  The Beaudry Group has firmly established itself as a leader in the landscape design and build industry. We work closely with our clients to develop an intimate understanding of the home or buildings architecture and site conditions and follow a process from concept to completion to turn a vision into reality. We're proud to be recognized throughout the the community for our landscaping services including lawn maintenance and snow removal for homeowners, condominium corporations, government facilities and other businesses.

profile:
Steele Pools is based out of Oakville, ON.  We service Oakville, Burlington, Mississauga, Ancaster, Hamilton and Toronto.  We create custom swimming pools, water features, high end natural stonework, beautiful flagstone patios, outdoor kitchens, and more.   
We pride ourselves on using the highest quality products available and attention to even the smallest details in our workmanship.  
We specialize in Custom swimming pools and natural stonework.
We believe in quality over quantity and building a fantasy backyard oasis to last you and your family years to come.
